<PageTitle>B4 State Events Binding</PageTitle>

<h1>B4. State, Events, and Data Binding</h1>

<p>
	This sample focuses on state updates, event handling, and one/two-way binding in a Blazor Web App.
</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>State Counter</strong>: Demonstrates local state mutation after click and async events.</li>
	<li><strong>Binding Live</strong>: Demonstrates <code>@@bind</code>, <code>@@bind:event="oninput"</code>, and formatted binding.</li>
	<li><strong>Event Callback</strong>: Demonstrates child-to-parent notification with <code>EventCallback&lt;T&gt;</code>.</li>
</ul>
